    "Additionally, the ability to converse in a natural manner, provide relevant responses, and understand the emotional state of a human is one of the high-level cognitive skills that enables social bonding and coordination of actions (p. 13), making users develop trust in the application.",
    "GPT-3, which was used for this research, uses prompts to provide commands to the text-generation algorithm (see Methods section for more details).",
    "The primary difference between GPT-3 and ChatGPT is the nature of input-prompt-based for GPT-3 and dialog-based for ChatGPT.",
    "In both cases, input is key, because these algorithms parse the entire input phrase to determine the context.",
    "To understand how that is done, we need to look closely at the architecture of GPT."
